DESCRIPTION
.br
.in +5
VTTT is the X and O game popular in the early elementary grades.
Grid positions are defined by the numbers 1 through 9 as
presented when the game starts.
This version makes use of the cursor addressing capabilities
of most video terminals to present and update the playing grid.